metadata.editComments: That doesn't seem correct to me.
Based on the old comments which I saw in my email, this is supposed to be the drum solo. It shouldn't be here at all, but I have to at least sync the proper video so it doesn't break everything.

I am new to this, so I referred to the analytical work of musicologist, Alan W. Pollack (https://www.icce.rug.nl/~soundscapes/DATABASES/AWP/te.shtml). Pollack has analyzed every Beatles tune. My attempt tries to express Pollack's analysis as best I could fit it in Hook Pad.
